{"tid":12622,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國國會料今日促哇集拉隆功繼承皇位","createTime":"2016-11-29T17:30:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T18:14:20.000Z","uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dab50464f710d36cc02e7c33b6d49b3417216a41","tid":12622,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:30:07.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】泰王普密蓬在上月13日去世，泰國國會今日召開特別會議，預料會促請皇儲哇集拉隆功繼承皇位。<br />\n　　根據憲法規定的繼承皇位程序，政府內閣將要求國會促請皇儲繼位；皇儲必須接受邀請，才可成為新一任泰王。據知哇集拉隆功現時身處德國，會在今個星期稍後返回泰國。<br />\n　　泰國在泰王普密蓬去世後，宣布全國守喪一年，哇集拉隆功以悼念父親為由要求推遲登基。外電早前報道，哇集拉隆功會在12月1日登基，但因為泰國仍在哀悼病逝的泰王普密蓬，哇集拉隆功會到明年才接受加冕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%96%99%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E4%BF%83%E5%93%87%E9%9B%86%E6%8B%89%E9%9A%86%E5%8A%9F%E7%B9%BC%E6%89%BF%E7%9A%87%E4%BD%8D-035100560.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%2599%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%2597%25A5%25E4%25BF%2583%25E5%2593%2587%25E9%259B%2586%25E6%258B%2589%25E9%259A%2586%25E5%258A%259F%25E7%25B9%25BC%25E6%2589%25BF%25E7%259A%2587%25E4%25BD%258D-035100560.html&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPHvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=079a46ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%96%99%E4%BB%8A%E6%97%A5%E4%BF%83%E5%93%87%E9%9B%86%E6%8B%89%E9%9A%86%E5%8A%9F%E7%B9%BC%E6%89%BF%E7%9A%87%E4%BD%8D-035100560.html</a>"},{"pid":"f7bdf0d44f9a5096e3915546c4ec750a47fb7aed","tid":12622,"uid":20332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:30:53.000Z","msg":"廢柴皇帝"},{"pid":"bf0a0a046792602a6337ce6fe3382d5bf9aaf529","tid":12622,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:07:47.000Z","msg":"依到有泰國巴打，我想問點睇"},{"pid":"a8102e25bb87be6779c0fa5cc776c59ef9432b30","tid":12622,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>依到有泰國巴打，我想問點睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都想知可以有得點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13646faa6c54ffcaf71eb9022701b3fcf108a8b8","tid":12622,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:14:20.000Z","msg":"想知下想唔想佢做皇帝定是撚但咁囉"}]}